Description: Fix resize/fullscreen rendering via full FBO composite pipeline
 Replace the old screen pass with a full FBO composite pipeline:
 pass 3 renders scene + vblur overlay into textureFinal at fixed
 fboWidth x fboHeight with explicit viewport and projection reset.
 The final screen pass letterboxes/pillarboxes textureFinal to preserve
 the original aspect ratio regardless of window/fullscreen size.
